<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>AmicBridge – A private bridge between borrowers, lenders and business partners</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network. We connect people who want to lend, borrow, invest or learn strategy on their own terms, with a strong focus on identity, clarity and trust.">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f5f7;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --text-muted: #6b7280;
      --primary: #2563eb;
      --primary-hover: #1d4ed8;
      --radius-lg: 12px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      --max-width: 1000px;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-main);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button { font-family: inherit; }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.9rem 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.4rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -0.12rem;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #2563eb;
      transition: width 0.15s ease-out;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

    .nav-cta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .nav-cta a { color: #2563eb; font-weight: 500; }

    .nav-cta .btn-small {
      padding: 0.45rem 0.95rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      background: #ffffff;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .nav-cta .btn-small:hover { background: #f3f4f6; }

    .hero {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
      padding: 3rem 0 3.2rem;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }

    .hero-text { max-width: 680px; }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.6vw + 1.2rem, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-body {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 1.6rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 0.68rem 1.3rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }

    .btn-secondary {
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
      padding: 0.68rem 1.3rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover { background: #f9fafb; }

    .btn-ghost {
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      color: #2563eb;
      padding: 0.68rem 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-footnote {
      margin-top: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 640px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .section-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .card-simple {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem 1.3rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .card-simple h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      color: var(--text-main);
    }

    .card-simple ul {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.1rem;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .card-simple li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.4rem 1.4rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    }

    .field {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .field label {
      color: #111827;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .field input,
    .field textarea,
    .field select {
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .field input:focus,
    .field textarea:focus,
    .field select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
    }

    .field small {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .field-inline {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .checkbox-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .checkbox-row input { margin-top: 0.15rem; }

    .form-note {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }

    .side-note {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: #f9fafb;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    footer .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    footer a { color: #4b5563; }

    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.2rem;
    }

    .step-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1rem 1rem 1.1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .step-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .step-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      color: var(--text-main);
    }

    .step-text {
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    @media (max-width: 880px) {
      .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr); }
      .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero { border-radius: 0; margin-top: 0.8rem; }
      .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <div class="shell nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <div class="logo-mark">A</div>
        <div class="logo-text">AmicBridge</div>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a>
        <a href="#trust">Trust &amp; profile</a>
        <a href="#business">Business &amp; profit sharing</a>
        <a href="#strategy">Investment strategy</a>
        <a href="/create-profile">Create profile</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <a href="#contact">Sign in</a>
        <button class="btn-small" type="button" id="btn-join-nav">Join the network</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="about">
      <div class="shell hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            A private, trusted bridge between borrowers, lenders and business partners.
          </h1>

          <!-- Your new line -->
          <p class="hero-body" style="font-weight:600; color:#111827;">
            Grow your money with investments big or small.
          </p>

          <p class="hero-body">
            AmicBridge is a private network that connects people who want to lend and borrow money on
            their own terms. We don’t control the deal – we help you find real people who could become
            valuable financial partners for the future, whether that is through lending, shared profit,
            or long-term business collaboration.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <button class="btn-primary" type="button" id="btn-request-loan">
              Request a loan
            </button>
            <button class="btn-secondary" type="button" id="btn-offer-lending">
              Offer lending
            </button>
            <button class="btn-ghost" type="button" id="btn-business-invest">
              Seek business investment / share profit
            </button>
            <button class="btn-ghost" type="button" id="btn-invest-strategy">
              Ask about investment strategy
            </button>
            <button class="btn-ghost" type="button" id="btn-create-profile">
              Create profile
            </button>
          </div>

          <p class="hero-footnote">
            AmicBridge never holds funds or crypto, never signs loan or investment contracts, and never guarantees
            repayment, returns or matches. All agreements and transfers happen directly between members, who must
            make their own decisions, assessments and compliance checks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
